name: Picton Mahoney Fortified Special Situations Alternative Fund
longDescription: The proposed investment objective of the Fund is to maximize total return to unitholders through income and capital appreciation ETF seeks to invests primarily in event-driven situations in global fixed income while mitigating capital loss through shorting and other hedging strategies.
